    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i get that, but i'm not talking about getting drunk lol. just like a tiny bit of wine to take the edge off. i've heard people do it all the time to help them drift off. since the dose is small, wouldn't the risk be pretty minimal? it just seems like it would make the diazepam more effective for my insomnia.",
